ed, we introduce a suitable measure for the contrast of these maxima. The\nresults are condensed into a finite-temperature crossover diagram for hard-core\nbosons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Jan 2019 21:11:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 2 Feb 2019 18:01:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 5 May 2019 17:00:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-07"}
